<h3 id="head-aa07953722cf47f5ac8305861bc6173a9a42cc5c">About this FAQ</h3>
<p>
This FAQ is mean to be a companion to the standard ToME help files for using inscriptions, macros, and keymaps. The ToME help files which also describe them are listed in the "References" section. 
</p>
<p>
This documentation is for ToME, version 4.2.x. <em><a href="./MayLith">MayLith</a>: uhh???</em> 
</p>
<p>
<strong>SPOILER ALERT</strong> 
</p>
<p>
This document gives some information on how the game does or doesn't work that might be considered spoiling. Most players advanced enough to use macros probably won't notice. 
</p>

